{"title_page": "Ernest Reed", "text_new": "'''Ernest Samuel Reed''' was a [[Canadians|Canadian]] [[Anglican]] [[bishop]] in the second half of the 20th century.<ref>[http://www.ottawa.anglican.ca/Past_Bishops.htmlAnglican Bishops of Ottawa]{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\nReed was educated at the [[University of Manitoba]]<ref>[[Who's Who|\"Who was Who\"]] 1897-1990 London, [[A & C Black]], 1991 {{ISBN|0-7136-3457-X}}</ref> and ordained in 1931.<ref>[[Crockford's Clerical Directory]]1940-41 Oxford, [[OUP]],1941</ref> He began his ordained ministry with a [[Curate|curacy]] in [[Rupertsland]] and then held [[Vicar|incumbencies]] at [[Cowansville]], [[Rouyn-Noranda|Noranda]] and [[Montreal]] after which he was [[Archdeacon]]  of [[Gasp\u00e9, Quebec|Gasp\u00e9]]. From 1954 until his death in 1970 he was the 4th [[Anglican Diocese of Ottawa|Bishop of Ottawa]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210059&rt=1&bill=1 |title=Archives Canada (1) |access-date=2009-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725185032/http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210059&rt=1&bill=1 |archive-date=2011-07-25 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210051&rt=1&bill=1 |title=Archives Canada (2) |access-date=2009-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725185045/http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210051&rt=1&bill=1 |archive-date=2011-07-25 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-rel|ac}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Robert Jefferson]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Anglican Diocese of Ottawa|Bishop of Ottawa]]|years=1954 &ndash;1970}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[William James Robinson]]}} \n{{end}}\n\n{{Anglican bishops of Ottawa}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Reed, Ernest Samuel}}\n[[Category:Canadian people of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:University of Manitoba alumni]]\n[[Category:Canadian Anglican priests]]\n[[Category:Anglican archdeacons in North America]]\n[[Category:Anglican bishops of Ottawa]]\n[[Category:20th-century Anglican bishops]]\n[[Category:1970 deaths]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n\n\n{{Canada-Anglican-bishop-stub}}\n", "text_old": "'''Ernest Samuel Reed''' was a [[Canadians|Canadian]] [[Anglican]] [[bishop]] in the second half of the 20th century.<ref>[http://www.ottawa.anglican.ca/Past_Bishops.htmlAnglican Bishops of Ottawa]{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n\nReed was educated at the [[University of Manitoba]]<ref>[[Who's Who|\"Who was Who\"]] 1897-1990 London, [[A & C Black]], 1991 {{ISBN|0-7136-3457-X}}</ref> and ordained in 1931.<ref>[[Crockford's Clerical Directory]]1940-41 Oxford, [[OUP]],1941</ref> He began his ordained ministry with a [[Curate|curacy]] in [[Rupertsland]] and then held [[Vicar|incumbencies]] at [[Cowansville]], [[Rouyn-Noranda|Noranda]] and [[Montreal]] after which he was [[Archdeacon]]  of [[Gasp\u00e9, Quebec|Gasp\u00e9]]. From 1954 until his death in 1970 he was the 4th [[Anglican Diocese of Ottawa|Bishop of Ottawa]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210059&rt=1&bill=1 |title=Archives Canada (1) |access-date=2009-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725185032/http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210059&rt=1&bill=1 |archive-date=2011-07-25 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210051&rt=1&bill=1 |title=Archives Canada (2) |access-date=2009-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725185045/http://www.archivescanada.ca/english/search/ItemDisplay.asp?sessionKey=999999999_142&l=0&lvl=1&v=0&coll=1&itm=210051&rt=1&bill=1 |archive-date=2011-07-25 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-rel|ac}}\n{{s-bef|before=Robert Jefferson}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Anglican Diocese of Ottawa|Bishop of Ottawa]]|years=1954 &ndash;1970}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[William James Robinson]]}} \n{{end}}\n\n{{Anglican bishops of Ottawa}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Reed, Ernest Samuel}}\n[[Category:Canadian people of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:University of Manitoba alumni]]\n[[Category:Canadian Anglican priests]]\n[[Category:Anglican archdeacons in North America]]\n[[Category:Anglican bishops of Ottawa]]\n[[Category:20th-century Anglican bishops]]\n[[Category:1970 deaths]]\n[[Category:Year of birth missing]]\n\n\n{{Canada-Anglican-bishop-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Amqui", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:+wikilink", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernest_Reed"}
